Let's meet at 5:30 p.m. and eat dinner at Lamprey's River Tavern (at 110 Main St, Newmarket), then travel nearby to the band at Rockingham Ballroom, 22 Ashswamp Rd, Newmarket, NH.

Eat, drink, dance and be merry with the Jumbo Circus Peanuts New Orleans-Style Live Band. Every time we see this band we love them.

RSVPÂ by clicking on the "Register Now and Join the Party" at www.exetertheater.org/announcement.html ($10 entry fee for the band.)
